KW  - Regime shifts
KW  - Reserves
AB  - Many Latin American countries appear locked into cycles of reserve loss, devaluation and temporary reserve gains. This paper shows how a dual exchange rate system with leakages may generate cycles in reserves and the premium between official and parallel exchange rates. We study the dynamics of these cycles and their asymptotic behavior both analytically and numerically.
